<topic id='business_definition_indirect_activity.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Indirect Activity - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_indirect_activity">Indirect Activity</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_indirect_activity">Indirect Activity</xref>
 is 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
, with the specific purpose of supporting the care of a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
, but where the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 is not present.  </p>
  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_indirect_activity">Indirect Activity</xref>
 may take place between a:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
            <p>
and another 
                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
            <p>and another professional such as a teacher</p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
            <p>
and another 
                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>
, such as a family member or 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_carer">Carer</xref>
, not acting in the capacity of a 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_patient_proxy">Patient Proxy</xref>
.        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
Examples of 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_indirect_activity">Indirect Activity</xref>
 include a:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
            <p>
 seeking advice from another 
                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 regarding the treatment or diagnosis of a specific 
                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
            <p>
providing training to a teacher to support the medical needs of a specific 
                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
            <p>
discussing the care of a 
                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 with another 
                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 as part of a 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_multidisciplinary_team_meeting">Multidisciplinary Team Meeting</xref>
, where the 
                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 is not present        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
            <p>
providing training or advice to a family member or a 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_carer">Carer</xref>
 to support the medical needs of a specific 
                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
.        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_indirect_activity">Indirect Activity</xref>
 does not include discussions regarding groups of 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 or other administrative activities such as writing up of notes or travel.  </p>
  <p>
Note: For the 
    <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_mental_health_services_data_set">Mental Health Services Data Set</xref>
, contacts between a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 and a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_patient_proxy">Patient Proxy</xref>
 should be captured as a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_contact">CARE CONTACT</xref>
 with the 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_care_contact_subject">CARE CONTACT SUBJECT</xref>
 set to '
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_patient_proxy">Patient Proxy</xref>
'.  </p>

